column5: Yes he,s 25 today,little younger then 29.LOL  Since buying him his float rod he has really gotten in to the river thang. Spoiled brat. LOL           Happy B-DAY to you both.

Got a couple new lures, a BPS card, a dozen red roses, some perfume, a gift card to the "The Fish House" restaurant and some nice jewellery.  It was a great birthday.  Wish your son the best B  Joey
